#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:45
#: 92455e8a4b9a40a2be52642788424308
msgid "Node transitions follow two rules: 1) if a :math:`S` state node has :math:`I` state neighbors, each :math:`I` state neighbor transmits the infection to the :math:`S` state node with probability :math:`\\beta`; 2) the :math:`I` state node is recovered to the :math:`R` state with probability :math:`1`."
msgstr ""

